				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-440666#post-2826548</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-440666/scp-1201#post-2826548</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 19 May 2017 17:26:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deviant Logic</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3019212</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Standing on its own, this would be a weird and kinda goofy bit of&#8230;something, and maybe briefly amusing, although it would have done better as some standalone YouTube animation. As an SCP it's completely inappropriate though. It really doesn't fit at all, and&#8230;let's just face it, there's enough stupid crap making fun of gamer attitudes as it is, and this one isn't even particularly well done considering the low-hanging fruit.</p> <p>Also, the logs being chronologically out of order makes no sense and brings up the 'Foundation looks stupid' stuff for no reason. It's actually distracting, and there's nothing gained by changing that order away from chronological.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
