				<pubDate>Mon, 06 Feb 2012 06:16:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Uncandescent</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>588650</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Okay, this is a cartoon. These are events that can and should only occur in an animated medium. I am completely and utterly unable to take this seriously. If that's what you were going for, you did a frankly amazing job. But this is simply too hilarious to be an actual SCP.</p> <p>I'm not saying that this is bad. I'm saying that this is way too silly. The only way this could be any more of a Looney Toons cartoon is if 1202-2 mistook a sick of dynamite for a hot dog, had it blow up in his face, made a smart-ass quip, and then went&#8230; and&#8230;</p> <p>Regenerated his injuries. Son of a bitch.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
